      "settings": {
        "abt_img": "shopify://shop_images/transforming_wellness1.png",
        "desc1": "<p>We’re taking wellness to the next level with innovative technologies and smart formulations. Our NanoDrop Technology<strong> </strong>delivers nutrients with over 95% bioavailability, ensuring your body gets what it needs quickly and efficiently. With nanocarrier systems like liposomes and solid lipid nanoparticles, we’ve found a way to maximize absorption and stability for every active ingredient. </p><p>Our encapsulation technology locks in the goodness, while our opaque gummies<strong> </strong>bring you real fruit flavors, natural colors, and a satisfying chew without the medicinal aftertaste. Plus, everything is designed for high bioavailability, so nothing goes to waste!</p>",
        "abt_heading": "Transforming Wellness with Cutting-Edge Science"
      }
    },
    "features_hm_WAd7RR": {
      "type": "features-hm",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Chew. Melt. Thrive",
        "desc": "<p>Mingo has curated dietary supplements by offering enjoyable and effective alternatives to traditional pill-based nutrients, making wellness on-the-go effortless. </p><p>Both GoGummies, the microencapsulated gummies, and MoMints, the bioavailable oral strips, provide significant benefits, packed with the perfect fusion of flavor and health.</p><p>Crafted with plant-based, soy-free ingredients, they are not only safe but also wholesome and delightful. Mingo’s health collections are not a task, they’re a nutrient treat!</p>"
      }
